// Orchicon Workflow entity (docs/02_Domain_Model.md §2.4, docs/09 §3.4).
//
// A Workflow is a composable execution plan referencing Workers and
// Steps. Workflows live at the project level (a Project's execution
// plan) or as reusable templates at the tenant level (project_id
// empty). A published Workflow version is immutable; edits create a new
// version (docs/02 §2.4).
//
// A Step is: id, kind (task | decision | approval | parallel |
// recover), ref (Worker reference or sub-workflow), depends_on (other
